    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. everything is just... falling apart. the planet is literally dying and we're all just sitting here pretending like there's a future to plan for. it feels so pointless to even try to build a life or care about anything when the whole world is just a sinking ship. what's even the point of being here?",
